 transition-colors\"><span class=\"text-xl font-black\">E</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mb-3\">Emergency Pest Control</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">Professional emergency pest control tailored to protect your property. We guarantee fast response times, expert technicians, and complete elimination of pests to restore your peace of mind.</p><a class=\"text-accent-500 font-bold text-sm inline-flex items-center hover:text-accent-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/emergency-pest-control\">Learn More <span class=\"ml-1 text-lg leading-none\">→</span></a></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all p-8 group\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-accent-500/10 rounded flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-accent-500 group-hover:bg-accent-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors\"><span class=\"text-xl font-black\">S</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mb-3\">Same Day Pest Control</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">Professional same day pest control tailored to protect your property. We guarantee fast response times, expert technicians, and complete elimination of pests to restore your peace of mind.</p><a class=\"text-accent-500 font-bold text-sm inline-flex items-center hover:text-accent-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/same-day-pest-control\">Learn More <span class=\"ml-1 text-lg leading-none\">→</span></a></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all p-8 group\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-accent-500/10 rounded flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-accent-500 group-hover:bg-accent-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors\"><span class=\"text-xl font-black\">R</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mb-3\">Residential Pest Control</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">Professiona