mers trust us to protect their homes and businesses.</p><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-accent-500 rounded flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-white text-xl font-bold\">1</div><div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 mb-1\">24/7 Availability</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">Pests don&#x27;t sleep, and neither do we. We&#x27;re available around the clock for emergency exterminations.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-accent-500 rounded flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-white text-xl font-bold\">2</div><div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 mb-1\">Eco-Friendly &amp; Safe</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">Our treatments are tough on pests but completely safe for your family, children, and pets.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-accent-500 rounded flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-white text-xl font-bold\">3</div><div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 mb-1\">Guaranteed Results</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">If the pests come back between scheduled treatments, we will re-treat your property at no extra cost.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"relative h-full min-h-[400px] rounded overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\"><img src=\"/images/media__1783510930934.jpg\" alt=\"Pest Control Technician\" class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 px-4 bg-surface-900 text-white border-y border-surface-800\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16\"><h4 class=\"text-accent-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-xs\">TESTIMONIALS</h4><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6\">What Our Customers Say About Us</h2><div class=\"w-24 h-1 bg-accent-500 mx-auto rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-surface-800 p-8 rounded border border-surface-700 relative\"><div class=\"text-yellow-400 mb-4 text-sm tracking-widest\">★★★★★</div><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed italic\">&quot;<!-- -->They arrived within 45 minutes of my call for a massive ant problem. The technician was polite, explained everything, and the ants were gone by the next day. Highly recommend!<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center text-surface-900 font-bold text-sm\">S</div><span class=\"font-bold text-white text-sm\">Sarah M.</span></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-800 p-8 rounded border border-surface-700 relative\"><div class=\"text-yellow-400 mb-4 text-sm tracking-widest\">★★★★★</div><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed italic\">&quot;<!-- -->We had a severe termite issue that other companies couldn&#x27;t fix. The team from batyspestcontrol did a thorough inspection and treatment. We haven&#x27;t seen a termite since. True professionals.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center text-surface-900 font-bold text-sm\">J</div><span class=\"font-bold text-white text-sm\">John D.</span></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-800 p-8 rounded border border-surface-700 relative\"><div class=\"text-yellow-400 mb-4 text-sm tracking-widest\">★★★★★</div><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed italic\">&quot;<!-- -->I love that they use eco-friendly products. Having a dog and a toddler, safety was my number one concern. The pest control was highly effective and completely safe. 5 stars!<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center text-surface-900 font-bold text-sm\">E</div><span class=\"font-bold text-white text-sm\">Emily R.</span></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 px-4 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\"><div><h4 class=\"text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-xs\">FAQS</h4><h2 class=\"text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-surface-900 mb-8 leading-tight\">Pest Control Services FAQs</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><details class=\"group border border-gray-200 rounded bg-gray-50 open:bg-white transition-colors\"><summary class=\"font-bold text-surface-900 p-5 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm md:text-base\">How quickly can you arrive?<span class=\"text-accent-500 font-bold text-xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform\">+</span></summary><div class=\"px-5 pb-5 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4\">We offer 24/7 emergency dispatch. In most areas, we can have a technician at your property within 60-90 minutes of your call.</div></details><details class=\"group border border-gray-200 rounded bg-gray-50 open:bg-white transition-colors\"><summary class=\"font-bold text-surface-900 p-5 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm md:text-base\">Are your treatments safe for pets?<span class=\"text-accent-500 font-bold text-xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform\">+</span></summary><div class=\"px-5 pb-5 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4\">Yes. We prioritize the safety of your family and pets. We use eco-friendly and pet-safe products, applied strictly according to safety guidelines.</div></details><details class=\"group border border-gray-200 rounded bg-gray-50 open:bg-white transition-colors\"><summary class=\"font-bold text-surface-900 p-5 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm md:text-base\">Do I need to leave my house during treatment?<span class=\"text-accent-500 font-bold text-xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform\">+</span></summary><div class=\"px-5 pb-5 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4\">For most routine treatments, you do not need to leave. However, for certain intensive treatments like bed bug extermination or heavy fumigation, we will advise you on the necessary vacancy period.</div></details><details class=\"group border border-gray-200 rounded bg-gray-50 open:bg-white transition-colors\"><summary class=\"font-bold text-surface-900 p-5 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm md:text-base\">Is there a guarantee on your work?<span class=\"text-accent-500 font-bold text-xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform\">+</span></summary><div class=\"px-5 pb-5 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4\">Yes, we provide a 100% satisfaction guarantee. If pests return between your scheduled services, we will re-treat the area at no additional cost.</div></details></div></div><div class=\"relative h-full min-h-[500px] rounded overflow-hidden shadow-xl\"><img src=\"/images/media__1783510931195.jpg\" alt=\"Customer Service\" class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 px-4 bg-surface-900 text-white border-y border-surface-800\" id=\"areas-we-serve\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16\"><h4 class=\"text-accent-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-xs\">LOCATIONS</h4><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6\">Pest Control Services in Major Cities &amp; Surrounding Areas</h2><div class=\"w-24 h-1 bg-accent-500 mx-auto rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-3\"><a class=\"bg-surface-800 border border-surface-700 hover:border-accent-500 text-white font-semibold px-4 py-4 rounded transition-all text-center flex flex-col items-center gap-2 group text-sm\" href=\"https://ak.batyspestcontrol.com\"><span class=\"text-accent-500 text-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">📍</span>A